  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-64 is-title1-64 is-title-bold\">2024獵豹學子錄取科學班人數再創高峰<br />\n（至少23人）!!!</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">錄取建科人數達12人 佔錄取人數近四成!!<br />\n<br />\n獵豹學子錄取名單<br />\n*建科<br />\n詹緯濬 賴敬宇 林秉坤 鄧靖懷 涂皓宇 張庭溱 黃楷博 蘇冠宇 王昱閎 吳耘丞 彭耀霆 尤耀星<br />\n（數位同學錄取分數超過190）<br />\n<br />\n*北一女科<br />\n吳家瑩 陳芃華 陳品妍<br />\n<br />\n*中一中科<br />\n劉恩瑋 陳煜中<br />\n<br />\n*南一中科<br />\n蘇程玹<br />\n<br />\n*雄中科<br />\n歐宸睿 余偲弘 葉承宇<br />\n<br />\n*附中科<br />\n江品綸 侯宇誠<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n今年是獵豹學子大放光芒的一年。<br />\n除了在國內外升學、各項竟賽都創下輝煌的佳績，遙遙領先其他機構（IJSO國中科奧金牌佔台灣半數，AMC8/10/12滿分三冠王…）。<br />\n這些同學參與的獵豹課程並非短期的模考衝刺訓練，而是紮實的數理資優培訓課程<br />\n（J/FJ, GM, S, FS, Sci, AMC, FUC…)。<br />\n我們今年推出的<span style=\"background-color:#dddddd;\">科學班/數資班終極備考課程【FA00 】</span>是獵豹六位名師精心籌劃的壓箱之作，專門為有志於科學班/數資班的學生設計。<br />\n透過最專業、最科學的訓練和專家模式的思維啟發，把學生從高手培養成真正的頂尖高手，從Good升級至Excellent，讓他們在競爭激烈的科學班/數資班的考試中，一騎絕塵，輕鬆過關！<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\nFA00課程【<span style=\"color:#e74c3c;\">目標&amp;性質</span>】：<br />\n1. 科學班/數資班入學考 數學備考終極課程<br />\n2. 高階競賽基礎課程<br />\n3. 頂尖數學高手的必備養成教育<br />\n<br />\nFA00課程【<span style=\"color:#e74c3c;\">入學背景&amp;條件</span>】<br />\n1. 具備國中數學課綱知識<br />\n2. 具備國中數理資優生的學習能力<br />\n3. 對數學充滿熱情。<br />\n<span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">不畏挫折,喜歡挑戰困難</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/posts/1445635029722511/\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">https://www.facebook.com/share/p/RvMdhjZGDBnwd6xN/?mibextid=K35XfP</span></a><span style=\"color:#3498db;\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUh-V1H1SzEwb1ztdNDz-koehIuBm_RVVPB7ryDV_dmc2qqzUiC0ohGVGLpUimYNgBK5mzuzwBUnhcpchQbA282yA47UOrdRFPe9Ej19O133shkI5SbVMrkM0d4R3pVFzfFsi-2uFLu8F9AU6PT0IBm68jQw1lC1d4LVGXKvH-iOg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\"><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">#建中科學班</span></a><span style=\"color:#3498db;\"> </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUh-V1H1SzEwb1ztdNDz-koehIuBm_RVVPB7ryDV_dmc2qqzUiC0ohGVGLpUimYNgBK5mzuzwBUnhcpchQbA282yA47UOrdRFPe9Ej19O133shkI5SbVMrkM0d4R3pVFzfFsi-2uFLu8F9AU6PT0IBm68jQw1lC1d4LVGXKvH-iOg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\"><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">#北一女科學班</span></a><span style=\"color:#3498db;\"> </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E9%99%84%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUh-V1H1SzEwb1ztdNDz-koehIuBm_RVVPB7ryDV_dmc2qqzUiC0ohGVGLpUimYNgBK5mzuzwBUnhcpchQbA282yA47UOrdRFPe9Ej19O133shkI5SbVMrkM0d4R3pVFzfFsi-2uFLu8F9AU6PT0IBm68jQw1lC1d4LVGXKvH-iOg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\"><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">#附中科學班</span></a><span style=\"color:#3498db;\"> </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUh-V1H1SzEwb1ztdNDz-koehIuBm_RVVPB7ryDV_dmc2qqzUiC0ohGVGLpUimYNgBK5mzuzwBUnhcpchQbA282yA47UOrdRFPe9Ej19O133shkI5SbVMrkM0d4R3pVFzfFsi-2uFLu8F9AU6PT0IBm68jQw1lC1d4LVGXKvH-iOg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\"><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">#中一中科學班</span></a><span style=\"color:#3498db;\"> </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUh-V1H1SzEwb1ztdNDz-koehIuBm_RVVPB7ryDV_dmc2qqzUiC0ohGVGLpUimYNgBK5mzuzwBUnhcpchQbA282yA47UOrdRFPe9Ej19O133shkI5SbVMrkM0d4R3pVFzfFsi-2uFLu8F9AU6PT0IBm68jQw1lC1d4LVGXKvH-iOg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\"><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">#南一中科學班</span></a><span style=\"color:#3498db;\"> </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E9%9B%84%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUh-V1H1SzEwb1ztdN